name: DigitalDashboardPlugin3DDensityPlotAdv
description: Visualization component for the old version of the DigitalDashboard. Expects to be connected as a child to the DigitalDashboard Webble. Plots 3D data in a sort of fake 3D (the front view in 2D, the side view in 2D, and the top view in 2D) and allows slicing out smaller blocks by clicking and draggin.
author: legacyDigitalDashboard
